body_html:
The inception model described in this file:
https://github.com/tensorflow/models/blob/master/inception/inception/slim/inception_model.py
corresponds to this tar-ball
http://download.tensorflow.org/models/image/imagenet/inception-v3-2016-03-01.tar.gz

The inception model employed by retrain.py here:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/examples/image_retraining/retrain.py
is a different and older version of the model. That model is
http://download.tensorflow.org/models/image/imagenet/inception-2015-12-05.tgz

body:
The inception model described in this file:
https://github.com/tensorflow/models/blob/master/inception/inception/slim/inception_model.py
corresponds to this tar-ball
http://download.tensorflow.org/models/image/imagenet/inception-v3-2016-03-01.tar.gz

The inception model employed by retrain.py here:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/examples/image_retraining/retrain.py
is a *different and older* version of the model. That model is
http://download.tensorflow.org/models/image/imagenet/inception-2015-12-05.tgz
